# AI Bot Visibility

- **Route**: `GET /check?url=<url>` (url required, http/https only).
- **Response**: `{ url, disclaimer, crawlers[], summary: { allowed[], blocked[], notSpecified[] } }`. Reports per-crawler status (allowed, blocked, not_specified) from robots.txt and page-level signals.
- **Bindings**: None.
- **Utils**: `validateUrl`, fetch of page and robots.txt; error shape `{ error, code }`.
